Rockpile  -  My Father's Place Roslyn NY 4th November 1978 FM FLAC

Rockpile were a British rock and roll group of the late 1970s and early 1980s, 
noted for their strong pub rock, rockabilly and power pop influences, and as a 
foundational influence on new wave.
